Name: Rocky and Bullwinkle
Overview: Based on the popular cartoon series, Rocky and Bullwinkle is an Xbox LIVE Arcade exclusive game that includes over 100 'micro-games' of various kinds. Some of the simplistic, swiftly playable-in-turn gameplay sections include juggling, shooting galleries, and a number of other Wario Ware-inspired micro-games, with characters including Dudley Do-Right, Fractured Fairy Tales, Peabody's Improbable History, and Aesop and Son.
